{
  "stem": "18450.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's K-I-B-U-T-Z.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a lot of young-- I would say 20 years old, or so, they went to work on the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they live on hard work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from over there, if it was a occasion going to Israel, they all went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So this was a big event that some 10 people or so went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they went to Israel to work on the-- you know, [INAUDIBLE], whatever, a kibbutzing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They went to a kibbutz in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, I don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I really don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I still have two girls who I met in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were the one they went to a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're not alive anymore, but they went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know who record them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was the-- the one who was, you know, from the organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was chosen, and he arranged it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not too much they could do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not involvement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing they started, the Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took him out and they send them to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] of course, they wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess that's German who were born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way I think of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In-- starts being a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could-- you know, you could smell it in the air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then came one, she was-- her name was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, that's what I heard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was in the Senate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she start looking for little troubles, like the slaughtering of cows shouldn't be the way it is, the ritual slaughtering.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then a lot of things that she objected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was the time when Hitler came to rise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she came to rise to her position this time.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
